I mean, I don't know,
I mean, this is...

40:01.732 --> 40:03.166
(sniffles)

40:03.201 --> 40:05.935
...it's a lot
for a girl to process.

40:05.970 --> 40:08.871
(laughing):
You're such an idiot.

40:08.906 --> 40:11.707
I love you.

40:11.742 --> 40:14.544
¶ A chance to discover... ¶

40:14.579 --> 40:16.612
I love you.

40:16.647 --> 40:18.648
Yes.

40:18.683 --> 40:20.783
Absolutely. What the hell? Yes.

40:20.818 --> 40:22.785
¶ Together we can do anything ¶

40:22.820 --> 40:24.720
¶ We believe it... ¶

