¶ You and me, we'll find a way ¶

40:31.629 --> 40:34.664
¶ Oh, the wonder that awaits ¶

40:34.699 --> 40:36.666
¶ Here we are,
forever starts... ¶

40:36.701 --> 40:39.635
Let's take a look at this thing.

40:39.670 --> 40:41.504
Well, I got to be honest,

40:41.539 --> 40:43.473
I thought that, uh,

40:43.508 --> 40:45.675
thought it'd have
a little more bling to it.

40:45.710 --> 40:48.511
Oh, no. You know me.

40:48.546 --> 40:50.813
I'm more bang than bling.

40:50.848 --> 40:51.814
That's right.

40:51.849 --> 40:53.516
Sunshine and gunpowder.

40:53.551 --> 40:54.517
(laughs)

